  Delta V^Pauli LDA-XC:                 -6.541335247616205       -177.9988         -4104.75        -17174.27
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Exchange:            0.328793082163397          8.9469           206.32           863.25
  Delta V^Pauli GGA-Correlation:        -0.458811449833573        -12.4849          -287.91         -1204.61
                                      --------------------     -----------       ----------      -----------
